      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project car. The engine currently has a blown head gasket and exhibits a noticeable rod knock, meaning it will likely require a full rebuild or replacement to be roadworthy again. Additionally, there is extensive rust through the floorboards and rear quarter panels, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn and stained. It is being sold strictly as-is, and the buyer will need to arrange for a tow as it is not safe to drive in its current state.",
