    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and mechanical reliability. This unit offers a balanced synthesis of performance and longevity, having been preserved in a condition that meets rigorous standards for its class. Its service history reflects a commitment to routine upkeep, ensuring a driving experience that remains both smooth and dependable. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this robust offering, which represents a significant value proposition for those prioritizing long-term utility and professional presentation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
