    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Everything works exactly like it should, and it's been well-maintained over the years. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
